{"tid":1162990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德晶片製造商英飛凌傳暫停供貨予華為","createTime":"2019-05-20T07:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T08:55:12.000Z","uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04c94cfe1f364c99173532913b7925f429d58ee0","tid":1162990,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"德國晶片製造商英飛凌(Infineon)據報暫時停止供貨予中國電訊商華為。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>此反映美國政府對華為實施封殺令的影響力，延伸至美國以外的企業</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n《日本經濟新聞》引述消息報道指出，英飛凌決定採取較為謹慎的做法，先停止立即出貨，該公司本周將舉行會議進一步討論事件，並且評估未來做法。現階段尚不清楚本周開會釐清法律問題後，英飛凌是否就會再與華為重啟業務往來。英飛凌先前賣給華為的產品，每年銷售額約1億美元(約7.8億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n英飛凌目前未對報道作出評論。<br />\n<br />\n英飛凌停止交貨，有可能帶動其他歐洲和亞洲的供應商，也採取更為審慎的措施。根據美國法規，未取得許可供貨給黑名單所列實體的公司，也將可能被列入黑名單。"},{"pid":"8b77bdd2eedff2a4dc6387608839b74f424a1549","tid":1162990,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"不打了，不打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f29c434c45dd651049c39efe9c4c2203b45784d","tid":1162990,"uid":31927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"德國下間會唔會leica<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5823aa985839b35948f4b09cb19fbf722d2cf1f","tid":1162990,"uid":187264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08072191adda4905e776082b476d05297fe60286","tid":1162990,"uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9f29c434c45dd651049c39efe9c4c2203b45784d","tid":1162990,"uid":31927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"德國下間會唔會leica<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi